monbulk.shared.Services
Class EnumerationElement

java.lang.Object
  monbulk.shared.Services.Element
      monbulk.shared.Services.EnumerationElement

public class EnumerationElement
extends Element

An enumeration element is an element that can be one of a set of values. The values can come from a dictionary or from a specific list of values stored in the element.
